Scope & limitations of this document:
1. Purpose
This method of statement covers the installation of flexible conduits and fittings as defined in the General Specification.

2. Scope of Works
This procedure will define the method to be used to ensure that flexible conduit installations and workmanship are correct and acceptable and shall conform to the Contract Documents and Specification
